bilingual.target: 这是一个惊人的力量测试。

bilingual.source: Music gave me strength and brought me relief.
bilingual.target: 音乐给了我力量，并带来了安慰。

bilingual.source: You have strength to do things if you have this.
bilingual.target: 如果你有这个，你就有力量做事。

bilingual.source: The little red fish's wisdom and friendship gave her strength.
bilingual.target: 小红鱼的智慧和友谊给了她力量。

bilingual.source: I was quite moved by their show of strength and grace.
bilingual.target: 他们展示的力量和优雅让我很感动。

bilingual.source: Cyclists need to have incredible strength in their legs in order to go up steep hills.
bilingual.target: 骑自行车的人需要有惊人的腿部力量才能爬上陡峭的山坡。

bilingual.source: Its artist, Han Gan, is known for his skill in capturing not only the physical features of the animal, but also its inner spirit and strength.
bilingual.target: 其画家韩干以捕捉动物的外貌特征以及内在精神和力量的技巧而闻名。

list.abstract: strength（英 [streŋθ]，美 [streŋθ]），英语单词，作名词为力、力量、实力等。短语搭配有strength training（力量训练）。例句有“I ran and did strength training.（我跑步并进行力量训练）”。 strength的近义词有force、might、excellence等；反义词有weakness、weak point、unpersuasiveness。复数是strengths。
力量（STR）是动漫《黑岩射手》中的角色，是神足由宇在异世界的意象体，她拥有红色的双瞳和一头白短发，带着包覆到唇边的黑色连帽，围脖上有白色火焰状花纹，双手装配有OgreArm，还有类似于金属脊椎状的尾巴。 力量与忍受不了现实痛苦的神足由宇本体互换了身份，从异世界中脱离后与麻陶等人成为了好朋友。

yingyinNormal.en: And that gives us strength. That strength is a powerful thing. It's not invisible. It radiates.
yingyinNormal.zh: 这给了我们力量，这股力量无比强大，不容忽视，光芒万丈。

yingyinNormal.en: "Greatness," he wrote, "lies not in being strong but in the right using of strength. He or she is the greatest whose strength carries up the most hearts by the attraction of his own."
yingyinNormal.zh: 他写道:“伟大并非在于力量的强大，而是你如何地去正确的使用你的力量。所有伟大的人，无论男女，将自己的魅力化作力量，影响周围的人。

yingyinNormal.en: I place my faith in God to give me purpose. I put my hope in you to give me strength.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我相信上帝会给我目标。我希望你们给我力量。

yingyinNormal.en: But there is more than just our deal for me to consider. I need to show strength.
yingyinNormal.zh: 但我要考虑的不仅是我们的协议，我得显示出力量。

yingyinNormal.en: These stones, it seems, can only be brandished by beings of extraordinary strength. Observe.
yingyinNormal.zh: 这些宝石，只有具超强力量的个体才能驾驭，请看。

yingyinNormal.en: These are fighters. They have been bred for war. Our Enemy has summoned his full strength.
yingyinNormal.zh: 他们都是战士，就是为战争而生，大敌已经动用了全部力量。
yingyinNormal.videoNameEn: 《The Hobbit: The Battle of the Five Armies》

yingyinNormal.en: Because dragons symbolize power and strength and they are, they are the strongest prawn in the ocean.
yingyinNormal.zh: 因为龙代表着力量与权力，它们也是，它们是海中最强大的虾。

yingyinNormal.en: I talked about our collective strength, black and white, coming together during times of crisis.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我提到了我们集体的力量，无论是黑人还是白人，在危机时刻走到一起。

yingyinNormal.en: Yes, actually. I wanted to convey sheer size. And size means stability, luxury and above all, strength.
yingyinNormal.zh: 是的，取它"硕大无比"的意思，大表示可靠，豪华，特别是力量。

yingyinNormal.en: And in her memory, we will all find strength to rid Panem of it's oppressors and be safe.
yingyinNormal.zh: 将她铭记于心，我们终将寻找到让施惠国摆脱其压迫者的力量，过上安稳的生活。

yingyinNormal.en: And so today, you risk yourself? I fulfill my duty. Rally my people. To inspire your strength.
yingyinNormal.zh: 所以今天，你是在冒险吗？这是我的责任，鼓舞人民的士气，激发你的力量。

yingyinNormal.en: Everything must seem so fragile to you since the scale of your strength has expanded one thousand times.
yingyinNormal.zh: 一切对于你来说都太脆弱了，因为你的力量已经扩大为原来的一千倍。

yingyinNormal.en: Traditionally, the dragon was a sign of strength and power and it was often used by China's emperors as their own symbol.
yingyinNormal.zh: 传统上，龙象征着力量和权力，中国的皇帝经常拿它作为自己的象征。

yingyinNormal.en: And when we do, we must hand the baton to the young. To those who have the strength to carry on our work when we are gone.
yingyinNormal.zh: 到那时，我们就得把接力棒交给下一代。那些等我们离世后，有力量继续我们事业的人。

yingyinNormal.en: If you wake up one morning with 1,000 times the strength you had the night before, how will you handle delicate day-to-day tasks?
yingyinNormal.zh: 如果某天早上你醒来发现你的力量是昨晚的一千倍，你该如何处理那些日常的精细活？

yingyinNormal.en: When people face a challenge they sometimes talk about taking a deep breath to find courage or strength. In fact, the word 'inspire' literally means 'to breathe in'.
yingyinNormal.zh: 人们常说，在遇到困难时要深吸一口气并找到勇气和力量。事实上，“激励”这个词也有“吸气”的意思。

yingyinNormal.en: I often draw strength from meeting ordinary people doing extraordinary things: volunteers, carers, community organizers and good neighbors; unsung heroes whose quiet dedication makes them special.
yingyinNormal.zh: 志愿者，护工，社工，友善的邻居，每次与这些作出伟大贡献的平凡人会面，都会给予我无穷力量。这些鲜少被歌颂的英雄，正是他们的默默奉献让他们变得与众不同。

yingyinNormal.en: Don't you think that we should all have a weapon like that? No. You simply lack the strength to wield them. Your bodies would crumble as your minds collapsed into madness. Is it weird that I wanna do it even more now? A little bit, yeah.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你不觉得我们每个人都应该弄把那样的武器吗？不。你们没有驾驭它们的力量。你们的身体会碎裂思维会崩溃甚至疯掉。我现在更想要了会不会很奇怪？没错，是有一点。

yingyinNormal.en: Sir? We need to respond to strength with strength.
yingyinNormal.zh: 先生？我们得以暴制暴。

yingyinNormal.en: Sorry. I don't know my own strength yet.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我不知道我力气这么大。

<highlight> 考频分布</highlight>

<highlight> 考纲释义</highlight>

sense_info_list.en: the quality or state of being physically strong
sense_info_list.zh: 力量; 体力; 力气

examination_example.sentence: The most immediate changes will be observed in skill level, <highlight>strength</highlight> and inches lost.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 最直接的变化将体现在技能水平、力量和减掉的英寸数上。

examination_example.sentence: I believe it is precisely this permanent coexistence of metaphysical message through physical means that is the <highlight>strength</highlight> of music.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 我相信，正是这种通过物理手段的形而上信息的永久共存，才是音乐的力量所在。

examination_example.sentence: When nursery colours were introduced, pink was actually considered the more masculine colour, a pastel version of red, which was associated with <highlight>strength</highlight>.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 当托儿所的颜色被引入时，粉红色实际上被认为是更阳刚的颜色，是红色的粉饰版，与力量有关。

sense_info_list.en: the power and influence that someone/something has

examination_example.sentence: Cooper and her colleagues argue that a "town of culture" award could increase the economic <highlight>strength</highlight> of Britain's towns.
examination_example.sentence_trans: Cooper 和她的同事认为，“文化城镇”奖可以提高英国城镇的经济实力。

examination_example.sentence: Assess its <highlight>strength</highlight> impartially.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 公正地评估其实力。

examination_example.sentence: Most importantly, it constantly modifies and enhances the games you play to build on the <highlight>strengths</highlight> you are developing.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 最重要的是，它不断修改和加强你的游戏，以建立你正在发展的实力。

sense_info_list.en: a good or beneficial quality or attribute of a person or thing

examination_example.sentence: If left to themselves, such trends will diminish the relative <highlight>strength</highlight> of the English language in international education markets.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 如果任其发展，这种趋势将削弱英语在国际教育市场上的相对优势。

examination_example.sentence: At first glance this might seem like a <highlight>strength</highlight> that grants the ability to make judgments which are unbiased by external factors.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 乍看之下，这似乎是一种优点，它赋予人们做出不受外部因素影响的判断的能力。
